               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300218-150-cd839" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300218-150-off838 t18300218-150-cd839"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300218-150-victim1029" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Jones
                        <interp inst="t18300218-150-victim1029" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
